[There have been scattered cases of chikungunya virus infection in Papua New Guinea this year (2013). A few individuals who were infected there became ill in Australia, illustrating the risk of long-distance spread from these foci.

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Papua New Guinea can be accessed at http://healthmap.org/r/1KlS. - Mod.TY]

